title: Instructional Archives
cleaned_text: Many healthcare providers have not been trained to identify and treat signs and symptoms of vaccine reactions. In fact, a lot of healthcare providers send patients home without a diagnosis and these patients are silently suffering. This guide will help identify the most common symptoms and help you find treatment and support if you think you need it. If you are unsure, make an appointment with a telehealth provider to help rule out illness.
